{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1272419, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "呃", "timestamp": 1615907407, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272422, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按中文发音吧，反正都是拼音...", "timestamp": 1615907427, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272425, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "字正腔圆的“清华 University”", "timestamp": 1615907448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272426, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "遇上这种我都是按普通话发音", "timestamp": 1615907461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272430, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "善用搜索\n----\n为什么「清华」是「Tsinghua」？\n\n清华大学的前身是清华学堂，其中「清华」的英文表示来自清末对「清华园」的英译。在清朝的官话（地位类似于现在的普通话）中，尖团音尚未合流，当年的「清」还读作「cing」，用国际音标表示即为[ʦʰiŋ]。\n\n当时「艳压群芳」、最为流行的拼音方案为「威妥玛拼音方案」，以此方案表示清朝官话中「清」的读音为「ts'ing」，随后「邮政式拼音」对威妥玛方案进行了修改，取消了「送气符」（所谓送气符是指右上角那一撇），于是ts'ing变为了tsing，「清华」的英译成为了「Tsinghua」。", "timestamp": 1615907479, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272433, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "qinghua，老外读的不对那是因为他们发音不标准，", "timestamp": 1615907495, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272437, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 一些城市的名字也是用威妥玛拼音写的，我印象里好像读的时候怎么写的就怎么读？", "timestamp": 1615907531, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 啊这个来源我知道就是不知道现在该怎么读😂", "timestamp": 1615907598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272566, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "青瓜大学", "timestamp": 1615908642, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1272984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本来就是怎么写怎么读，你这个居然是哪来的？", "timestamp": 1615911811, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1273868, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我找了一些英文宣传片都是读成q或者tʃ……不过可能没找到最官方的？楼上各位也都说按中文的读，我也有些怀疑了，想问一下Grace这个结论是哪里支撑的啊😂", "timestamp": 1615939721, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1274986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 250940, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 让Google读就是那个音，但是我刚才翻了一下宣传片，好像还真是发的 tʃ …… 不好意思，我也震撼了", "timestamp": 1615955731, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 250940, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "英语问题求助，Tsinghua这个词在读的时候居然是按“Qinghua”那样，开头读成“tʃ”的音吗？萌新一直以为就应该按拼写的那样读成“ts”。要做presentatation，注意到了这个问题，不知道怎么读。", "timestamp": 1615907390, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1615955730, "url": "", "vote": {}}}